What our clients see

   Clickstream dashboard
   Advertising performance dashboards are driven by Ignition Ai's
   ground-breaking attribution and AI based automated optimisation.
   Providing detailed analysis of ad campaigns, customer pathways to
   conversion and including standardised media metrics such as impressions
   served, viewability, spend and number of clicks/conversions.
   View dashboard Request Info./Demo Presentation
   Clickstream dashboard
   iSite (clickstream) dashboards are built to client requirements to
   reflect key performance indicators. A client can have multiple
   dashboards that report on different subjects ranging from basket
   abandonment to conversion analysis. The default dashboard is Power BI
   however it can also be Qlik, Tableau or any other.
   View dashboard Request Info./Demo Presentation

